               stealing, on the <rs id="t18181028-19-cd119" type="crimeDate">1st of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-19-off118 t18181028-19-cd119"></join>, 27 yards of cotton, value 28s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18181028-19-victim203" type="victimName">
                           Edward 
